Hrothgar's Journey				TYPE:Incantation	SCHOOL:Conjuration	SUBSCHOOL:Teleportation		CLASSES:ALL=6[PREVARGTEQ:UA_VAR_USEINCANTATION,1]	COMPS:V, S, M, SC	CASTTIME:60 Minutes	RANGE:Touch	TARGETAREA:Caster plus four to twelve other creatures.	DURATION:Instantanous	SAVEINFO:Will negates (harmless)	SPELLRES:Yes	DESC:Hrothgar's journey is an incantation based on the tale of Hrothgar, a powerful barbarian hero from ages past. Skill Check: Knowledge (arcana) DC 20, 2 successes; Perform (oratory) DC 20, 4 successes. Failure: 5d6 points of fire damage to caster. Material Component: A windowless, thatched hut in a forest. Backlash Component: Severe heat. Extra Casters: Four required; they provide the dialogue for other characters in the epic of Hrothgar.	SOURCEPAGE:UA								

